exports[`generateL0Contract > produces a stable snapshot for the validated rig 1`] = `
"# wf

## How to run this workflow

Start by opening \`wf/research/SKILL.md\`. It is the entry point — read it before doing anything else.

Each node file names the next file to open, as a relative path. Follow that path — do not
guess, skip ahead, or jump to a later node. Treat the directory as the source of truth for
what happens next, not this file.

Expected order for the unconditional path through this workflow:

1. research
2. plan
3. review
4. build

Conditional branches may change this order — the node file you are on always wins over
this summary.

## Gates

Some transitions in this workflow are conditional on explicit approval. When a node file
says to wait for approval before continuing, stop and wait — do not proceed to the next
node on your own judgement.

## Setup commands

None — this is a static, portable export. No install step is required to read or follow it."
`;
